tissueExpression.summary: Most normal tissues showed moderate cytoplasmic positivity. The gall bladder and parts of the intestine displayed strong staining. Liver and lymphoid tissues were weakly stained.
Most normal tissues showed moderate cytoplasmic positivity. The gall bladder and parts of the intestine displayed strong staining. Liver and lymphoid tissues were weakly stained.

Malignant cells generally exhibited moderate cytoplasmic immunoreactivity. Cases of skin cancers and malignant gliomas showed strong cytoplasmic immunoreactivity. Most malignant lymphomas, testicular and renal cancers were weakly stained or negative.
